### 알림 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications?size=20
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 읽지 않은 알림 개수 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/unread-count
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 읽음 처리 (단건)
